room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: We had a very exciting time escaping from this room with less than one minute left. Thankfully we were teamed up with three smart, young, and enthusiastic people. Great fun working on the clues. We did ask for help a few times, and all six of us contributed. This was our second visit to an escape room. First time that we escaped. I highly recommend The Dig.

room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: We did the dig. Had a great time. Will be back to do the agency next. Can't wait for the new room to open.

room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: Super fun! My co-workers and I went as a team building exercise. We did The Dig room, and it was very fun! We made it out in about 46 minutes. Definitely want to go back and try the other rooms!
